{"tid":16478,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[招聘]跪求燒味舖人才（侍應/燒味師傅）","createTime":"2016-12-01T12:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T05:34:58.000Z","uid":1796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb467b67c43cd57b84573a360f04d6a722060eaf","tid":16478,"uid":1796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:47:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我老竇開左間燒味店<br />\n本身都有人做開斬料/燒野嘅師傅<br />\n但係因為佢脾氣實在太臭，成日鬧客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話又話唔聽，老竇一直想炒左佢<br />\n但係一直招聘/搵人都未搵到人頂佢個位<br />\n講緊搵左已經差唔多半年都仲未搵到<br />\n所以條友又繼續串柒柒留喺舖頭<br />\n<br />\n小弟想問下LIHKG 有冇巴打係做開燒味又搵緊工<br />\n有親戚朋友介紹都唔區㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有幾個職位都想請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返工地點係紅磡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現想請既職位有：<br />\n1. 燒味師傅<br />\n工作：燒野（豬/叉燒etc.)，斬料，企檔口<br />\n要求：乾淨唔好鬧客，有經驗<br />\n人工：～$20000/月 每月約4日假期<br />\n<br />\n2. 收銀侍應x2<br />\n工作：收銀，打包d 野比個客，執枱，幫師傅手整下d 野食<br />\n要求：老實，手腳快，肯做肯學就得<br />\n人工：～$15000/月 每月約4日假期<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果各位巴打有興趣，或者你嘅朋友/親戚有興趣，歡迎喺下面留個言 LINE 我先 :yamikaze3985<br />\n如果冇LINE 既都可以send 個 email 比我：<br />\n<br />\n再再再唔係既可以入以下link 留個名同電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfOwGIUihDjA3zD1dISS-6nHnK3u60nS-chNtUBuTh-cIPEFg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfOwGIUihDjA3zD1dISS-6nHnK3u60nS-chNtUBuTh-cIPEFg%2Fviewform&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uBpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=78c7951a\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfOwGIUihDjA3zD1dISS-6nHnK3u60nS-chNtUBuTh-cIPEFg/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n感謝各位巴打入黎睇呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26ac6a1ef60836ddd38da40677b96c1c13024a8","tid":16478,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim